Managing Environmnets
======================

https://conda.io/projects/conda/en/latest/user-guide/tasks/manage-environments.html#activating-an-environment

1. Create an Environment
conda create --name <my-env>

conda create -n <my-env> python=3.X

conda create -n <my-env> numpy


2. Activate an Environment
conda activate <my-env>


3. Deactivate an Environment
conda deactivate

4. Listing all Available Enviroments
conda info --envs

5. Viewing a list of the packages in an Environment
conda list -n <my-env>


6. Removing an Environment
conda remove --name <my-env> --all


